<br>
I propose only two things:<br>
<br>
One I think it has gotten to the point where we need to start using that calendar on Innoruuk.com. The<br>
Eqvault board is just way too overloaded with flames and etc. that is has become to difficult to see who<br>
has what reserved when.<br>
<br>
