guild can only do ONE plane a weekend. Exceptions to this would be say Saturday you did PoF, and after<br>
the raid you noticed PoH was not yet scheduled. Then I think it would be ok to go ahead and schedule PoH<br>
for the next day.<br>
<br>
I only propose these ideas because I think that they will help us all in the future. Look at the situation we<br>
have now. People are posting for plane raids ONE MONTH ahead of time. Thanks!<br>
